ence/Global_Objects/Function/displayName\"><code>Function.prototype.displayName</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/length\"><code>Function.prototype.length</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/name\"><code>Function.prototype.name</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/prototype\"><code>Function.prototype.prototype</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methoden</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/apply\"><code>Function.prototype.apply()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/bind\"><code>Function.prototype.bind()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/call\"><code>Function.prototype.call()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/toString\"><code>Function.prototype.toString()</code></a></li></ol></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Eigenschaften</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor\"><code>Object.prototype.constructor</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methoden</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Die <strong><code>Number.isNaN()</code></strong> Methode stellt fest, ob der Übergabewert <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/NaN\"><code>NaN</code></a> ist und der Typ des Parameters&nbsp; <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number\"><code>Number</code></a> ist . Dieses ist eine robustere Version der globalen Methode <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/isNaN\"><code>isNaN()</code></a></p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"692\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/number-isnan.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code>Number.isNaN(<var>testWert</var>)</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parameter","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"testwert\"><code>testWert</code></dt>\n <dd>Der Wert, der auf <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/NaN\"><code>NaN</code></a> getestet werden soll.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"rückgabewert","title":"Rückgabewert","isH3":true,"content":"<p><strong>true</strong> wenn der Wert <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/NaN\"><code>NaN</code></a> und der Typ <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number\"><code>Number</code></a> ist. Anderfalls <strong>false</strong>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beschreibung","title":"Beschreibung","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Weil beide Gleichheitsoperatoren, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators\"><code>==</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> und <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators\"><code>===</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, den Vergleich, ob <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/NaN\"><code>NaN</code></a> <em>gleich</em> <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/NaN\"><code>NaN</code></a> ist, zu <code>false </code>auswerten, hat die Methode <code>Number.isNaN()</code> an Bedeutung gewonnen. Diese Situation ist anders als bei allen anderen Vergleichen von Werten in JavaScript.</p>\n\n<p>Im Vergleich zu der globalen Methode <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/isNaN\"><code>isNaN()</code></a> hat die Methode <code>Number.isNaN()</code> nicht das Problem, dass Werte zu einer Nummer konvertiert werden. Das bedeutet, das Werte, die normalerweise zu <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/NaN\"><code>NaN</code></a> konvertiert würden, aber momentan nicht dem Wert <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/NaN\"><code>NaN</code></a> entsprechen, ohne Probleme der Methode übergeben werden können. Das wiederum bedeutet, dass nur Werte vom Typ <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number\"><code>Number</code></a>, die zudem <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/NaN\"><code>NaN</code></a> entsprechen <code>true </code>als Resultat haben.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>Number<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">isNaN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">NaN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>        <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\nNumber<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">isNaN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Number<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token number\">NaN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\nNumber<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">isNaN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>       <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Beispiele, bei denen isNaN() true zurück gibt</span>\nNumber<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">isNaN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'NaN'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>      <span class=\"token comment\">// false</span>\nNumber<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">isNaN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">undefined</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// false</span>\nNumber<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">isNaN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>         <span class=\"token comment\">// false</span>\nNumber<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">isNaN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'blabla'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>   <span class=\"token comment\">// false</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Diese alle geben false zurück</span>\nNumber<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">isNaN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nNumber<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">isNaN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nNumber<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">isNaN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">37</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nNumber<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">isNaN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'37'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nNumber<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">isNaN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'37.37'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nNumber<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">isNaN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nNumber<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">isNaN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">' '</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"polyfill","title":"Polyfill","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Das Folgende funktioniert, weil <code>NaN</code> der einzige Wert ist, welcher nicht gleich mit sich selbst ist.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>Number<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>isNaN <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Number<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>isNaN <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">value</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> value <span class=\"token operator\">!==</span> value<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-number.isnan\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Number.isnan' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Initiale Definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-number.isnan\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Number.isnan' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.Number.isNaN","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number/isNaN/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number\"><code>Number</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/isNaN\"><code>isNaN()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beschreibung","id":"beschreibung"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"beispiele"},{"text":"Polyfill","id":"polyfill"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Die Number.isNaN() Methode stellt fest, ob der Übergabewert NaN ist und der Typ des Parameters  Number ist . Dieses ist eine robustere Version der globalen Methode isNaN()","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Number.isNaN()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Number.isNaN()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Number.isNaN()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Number.isNaN()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Number.isNaN()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Number.isNaN()","locale":"pl","nati